description: Episode of Series "Feelings". Explores how children view their physical selves and how that relates to the whole self-image. Includes children describing how they look, the importance of differences for helping one develop a sense of self-identity and specific suggestions for liking oneself better. Suitable for upper secondary and tertiary levels.
